  "description": {
    "zh": "手枪是必不可少的工具，总是随身带一把备用的，总是可能发生或多或少的意外，你的武器卡弹，你用光弹药，你能想到的……不幸的是，对大多数操作员来说，并不是所有人都随身携带副武器，我猜你也属于这一类。真遗憾，这真的会让你的生命处于危险之中，而我仍然需要你，明白吗？\n\n最近当地的所有人渣都更活跃了，我需要有人在这里和那里解决一些问题，你能做到吗？既然我们说到手枪，你何不用你的副武器干掉一些人呢？让你熟悉一下这些东西，我们从一些西方手枪开始。我相信你从你信任的供应商那里弄到它们不会有任何麻烦，对吧？",
    "en": "Pistols are an essential tool, always have a backup on you, something more or less unexpected could always happen, your weapon jams, you run out of ammo, you name it... Unfortunately for most operators, not all of them carry a sidearm on them, I assume you also fall into this category. Shame, it could really put your life in danger, and I still need you, got that?\n\nAll the local scum has been more active lately, I need someone to solve a few problems here and there, can you do that? And while we are speaking of pistols, why don't you take out some of them with your sidearm? Gets you some training with these things, let's start with some western pistols. I'm sure you won't have any trouble getting them from your trusted vendors, right?"
  },
